abstract: U.S. Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said on Friday that he expects to begin negotiations with China on a so-called Phase 2 trade deal soon, with Washington and Beijing on the same page.
snippet: U.S. Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said on Friday that he expects to begin negotiations with China on a so-called Phase 2 trade deal soon, with Washington and Beijing on the same page.
lead_paragraph: DAVOS, Switzerland — U.S. Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said on Friday that he expects to begin negotiations with China on a so-called Phase 2 trade deal soon, with Washington and Beijing on the same page.
headline_main: U.S. Treasury Secretary Mnuchin Expects Next China Trade Talks in 'Near Future'
headline_print_headline: U.S. Treasury Secretary Mnuchin Expects Next China Trade Talks in 'Near Future'

abstract: Impeachment managers suggested that behavior is only one part of a longer cover-up, much of which took place behind the scenes before the House had even learned of the pressure campaign.
snippet: Impeachment managers suggested that behavior is only one part of a longer cover-up, much of which took place behind the scenes before the House had even learned of the pressure campaign.
lead_paragraph: The House impeachment managers are now at work on the heart of their task for the afternoon: stringing together, bit by bit, a story of how President Trump and lawyers around him tried to conceal his Ukraine pressure campaign.
headline_main: Managers piece together a story of an extensive cover-up.

abstract: The vice president’s trip to Israel and Italy gave him ample opportunities to counterprogram the news back home. But impeachment is a hard topic to outrun.
snippet: The vice president’s trip to Israel and Italy gave him ample opportunities to counterprogram the news back home. But impeachment is a hard topic to outrun.
lead_paragraph: VATICAN CITY — Over three days, Vice President Mike Pence joined world leaders in Israel to commemorate the liberation of Auschwitz, visited the American Embassy in Jerusalem with a White House invitation for Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu, and then moved on to Rome to meet the pope.

abstract: E-commerce has unleashed an increasing torrent of fake merchandise upon the world and private companies and the U.S. government must do more to address the problem, Trump administration officials said Friday as they released a plan aimed at cracking down on counterfeit goods.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — E-commerce has unleashed an increasing torrent of fake merchandise upon the world and private companies and the U.S. government must do more to address the problem, Trump administration officials said Friday as they released a plan aimed at cracking down on counterfeit goods.
headline_main: US Says e-Commerce Firms Need to Do More About Fake Goods
headline_print_headline: US Says e-Commerce Firms Need to Do More About Fake Goods

abstract: Two of the lawyers on President Donald Trump’s impeachment defense team have shared another client: Alan Dershowitz and Ken Starr both helped the late hedge fund manager and sex offender Jeffrey Epstein win a lenient sentence for abusing underaged girls.

abstract: Under that precedent, it could in theory take only 3 Republicans to call witnesses.
snippet: Under that precedent, it could in theory take only 3 Republicans to call witnesses.
lead_paragraph: A premise of the escalating debate over whether the Senate should vote to call witnesses is that four Republicans would need to support that idea. Along with the 47 members of the Democratic caucus, four Republican senators would create a 51-vote majority.

headline_main: 1868 precedent might let Roberts weigh in on witnesses.

abstract: The president’s legal team plans to use only a few hours to begin to lay out its case on a day when few people are watching.
snippet: The president’s legal team plans to use only a few hours to begin to lay out its case on a day when few people are watching.
lead_paragraph: President Trump’s legal team plans to make a brief appearance on Saturday, using only a few hours to begin to lay out its case on a day when few people are watching, according to people briefed on the plan.
headline_main: White House defense plans a brief appearance for Saturday.

abstract: Under the rules of the trial, the defense will be followed by a short debate on witnesses and documents, with perhaps a chance for short closing statements.
snippet: Under the rules of the trial, the defense will be followed by a short debate on witnesses and documents, with perhaps a chance for short closing statements.
lead_paragraph: As they circle around a now familiar set of facts and their time grows shorter, the Democratic House managers are turning a greater part of their attention to pre-emptively rebut what they expect will be the White House’s arguments.
headline_main: Managers try to rebut expected defense by White House.
byline_original: By Michael D. Shear and Nicholas Fandos
